Insider Activity


Individual




Lawrence J. Pope



Mr. Lawrence J. Pope is Chief Human Resources Officer & EVP-Administration at Halliburton Co.
Mr. Pope was previously employed as Senior Vice President-Administration by KBR, Inc. and a Director-Finance & Administration by Halliburton Energy Services Group.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Texas and an MBA from the Jesse H Jones Graduate School of Business.



